title: DEGO Ambassadors Election Proposal
body:
Dear DEGO Community,

We hereby elect Ambassadors based on candidates' proposals and hold a voting session. 
The applicants will call on the community to vote for themselves. Top 10 volunteers who receive most amount of votes will be elected as DEGO Ambassadors. They will interact with community members and assist the administrators in community management, maintenance and more for a better DEGO community.

 Estimated Duration of Ambassadors Program Phase I: 3 months 
 Community Vote Time: Nov. 23rd - Nov. 27th (UTC+0 13:00) 

Here attached with work proof reports of candidates that prove the candidate’s contribution to DEGO, please read it before casting a vote:
https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1XapbO5WqucztduURB8IRJOxZe5usHjtiO71iBl-Tplg/edit#gid=0

Best Regard,
DEGO Team
author: 0x20FE4B1eD95911487499e53355BB8f14a881D735
